---
title: Vietnamese Beef & Sesame Broccoli with Jasmine Rice
description: Get ready for a classic blend of delicious Asian flavours in this two-part stir-fry of Vietnamese beef and sesame broccoli.  It looks colourful and vibrant and tastes like a party in your mouth - just like the best meals should!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vietnamese-beef-sesame-broccoli-b2a662d8.jpg
